{"tid":1915012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色Youtuber圈定黃色圍爐圈？","createTime":"2020-03-08T02:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T03:22:46.000Z","uid":277406,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c197745bf1fa1ae3f9f1629ad378fc946e066a","tid":1915012,"uid":277406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:21:57.000Z","msg":"到底黃色Youtuber圈目的係圍爐取暖定係想做大個餅？<br />\n一個成功嘅Youtuber 當中一定有佢魅力之處<br />\n例如唱歌好好聽，煮野食好叻，又或者份人好搞笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在我而言黃色Youtuber圈想影響嘅係中間遊離派多過一班深黃派。因為深黃只會更深，深藍只會更藍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真正需要影響到嘅係港豬同埋淺黃淺藍派。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n然後到一啲關鍵時候，例如區議會等等，就係呢班Youtuber用自身魅力去影響佢嘅觀眾。<br />\n<br />\nSorry 講咁耐 都係想大家支持下我個channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要係籃球同音樂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TzpFQ5iqE7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTzpFQ5iqE7E&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bwwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=bbd20852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TzpFQ5iqE7E</a><br />\nig: wmguitarbasketball"},{"pid":"8e8889e3cec6d4eb34b09278b3af7b0d4015250e","tid":1915012,"uid":32008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:25:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"926e7f83fb0d34f08aee070794d694f962cc8bf1","tid":1915012,"uid":277406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e8889e3cec6d4eb34b09278b3af7b0d4015250e","tid":1915012,"uid":32008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT